data.text:
Rama V of Thailand was born 20 September 1853 in Bangkok, Thailand to Mongkut (1804-1868) and Rampoei Siriwong (1834-1862) and died 23 October 1910 Dusit District, Bangkok, Thailand (Dusit Palace) of unspecified causes. He married Sunandha Kumariratana (1860-1880) .
